frontMatter.title: Google Coding Interview With A Competitive Programmer
frontMatter.summary: In this video, I conduct a mock Google coding interview with a competitive programmer, Errichto. As a Google Software Engineer, I interviewed dozens of candidates. This is exactly the type of coding interview that you would get at Google or any other big tech company.  Check out the video we made on Errichto's channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y8VeyLG3NhY  Prepping for coding interviews? Practice with 77 video explanations of popular interview questions and a full-fledged coding workspace on AlgoExpert: https://www.algoexpert.io (use "clem" promo code for a discount!)
